  "steps": [
    "125ul of 20uM Primer F.",
    "1.25ul of 20uM Primer R.",
    "10ul Phusion Buffer (5x).",
    "1ul of 10mM dNTPs.",
    "0.5ul Template DNA. From miniprep, preferably from DH5alpha cells, but BL21 is still dam+ so it should be fine - 5ng starting template is plenty! (note: good range = 50 - 100 ng).",
